---
title: Shawarma-Spiced Lamb Sandwich with Dill Yogurt Sauce and Roast Potatoes
description: This stacked Shawarma-spiced lamb sammie is tasty and colourful! Savoury lamb patties are paired with roasted potatoes and a zingy dill yogurt sauce for an instant classic.
